{"tid":1093992,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"依家it個市真係好咗，唔到我地否認","createTime":"2019-04-06T03:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T01:03:10.000Z","uid":34884,"like":8,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"bf5a35fb2c079ca40482b20536c8b1181c31e8c7","tid":1093992,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:26:24.000Z","msg":"我好記得2016年，第一屆DSE既IT degree畢業生，如果白紙一張，fg人工大概係14-18k呢個位<br />\n<br />\n2017年，基本上fg都坐低16k<br />\n<br />\n去到2018年，已經個個講緊白紙一張fg 18k先叫合理<br />\n<br />\n而今年就因為有好多Startup都有補貼（一定要用落請畢業生到），就18k啲人都叫住你唔好頂爛市，個個都喺到講緊fg起碼要20k<br />\n<br />\n所以我認為依家it個市係真係上緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52595f8a0bba41b2bcfdd8c08563ce918cf86359","tid":1093992,"uid":34884,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:28:04.000Z","msg":"補充一句：以上講既數字都係講緊正正常常剩係讀完it degree既畢業生，即係冇相關工作經驗既fg<br />\n<br />\n如果有一定唔止呢個數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3baf80f9998a22c91dd42d0baaf5b3882212225","tid":1093992,"uid":33631,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:31:14.000Z","msg":"有冇graduate employment survey report嘅數參考下？<br />\n冇就收收皮先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話我fg 100k一個月都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e318dbf25447962d37bf6e086ee9e186ee6d018","tid":1093992,"uid":116097,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:33:08.000Z","msg":"唔好吹奏喇 個市爆喇"},{"pid":"234ded3ab19669a59d01a8508dd777edb91584a5","tid":1093992,"uid":186072,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:34:48.000Z","msg":"上星期先15k請左3個<br />\n樓主點睇"},{"pid":"2c19d972fcd2c2a7e12b42d605a27e7696ee9af9","tid":1093992,"uid":34884,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"quote":{"